MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 70c970a7d9f7d414994564bd048e8a6d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Generic_Compelling
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KBTV.Runtime::KBTV.Dialogue.CallerDialogueTemplate
  Topic: {fileID: 0}
  Legitimacy: 3
  Priority: 0
  Length: 12
  IntroLines:
  - Text: Vern, what I'm about to tell you could change everything.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've kept this secret for years. Tonight, I'm finally speaking out.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: They told me never to talk about this. But people deserve to know.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  DetailLines:
  - Text: I have proof. Documentation. Testimony. Everything they tried to suppress.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: What I witnessed changes our understanding of reality itself.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The implications are staggering. And they've known all along.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  DefenseLines:
  - Text: I've sacrificed everything to bring this forward. Why would I lie?
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: They've tried to silence me. That alone tells you I'm onto something.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The truth is undeniable. No matter how much they try to bury it.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  AcceptanceLines:
  - Text: You're one of the few who'll let the truth be heard.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The world is waking up, Vern. Thanks to people like you.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Finally. Someone who understands.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDetailLines:
  - Text: But that's not all. There's a deeper layer to this that I've never shared
      publicly.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The documents I recovered paint an even more disturbing picture.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've connected with others who've had similar experiences. The pattern
      is unmistakable.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDefenseLines:
  - Text: I have contingencies in place. If something happens to me, the information
      goes public.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: My credentials are verifiable. My record is clean. I have no reason to
      fabricate this.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The people who've tried to discredit me only prove how important this information
      is.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  ConclusionLines:
  - Text: Keep fighting the good fight, Vern. The truth will prevail.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Stay safe out there. They're always watching.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  - Text: This is just the beginning. More will come forward.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
